Package mvc

Class ActionChainData

java.lang.Object
mvc.ActionChainData
public class ActionChainData extends Object
This model class stores a user's saved action chain in a stage. It loads/ saves data by communicating with the ProgressionData object. Each ActionBlock is stored as a separate object.
Since:
March 11, 2024
Version:
1.0
Author:
Chun Ho Chan (Edward)

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    ActionChainData()
    Construct a clean action chain, includes padding and "Start" and "End" blocks.

    Note: Index 0 is "Unknown" block as padding, since "Start" block is at index 1.
